7/31/00
  After studying Ke's latest rate control code, I notice that he now uses 9
  freq cut matrices, depending on the reduction factor.  However, he has to
  copy the matrix to intra/er/FreqCutMatrix array because the assembly
  block2.s60 assumes the matrix is stored there.  However, if instead we
  modify the assembly so that intra/er/FreqCutMatrix is a pointer to the
  array, then we don't need to copy the matrix.

